Properties.Value:
DECLARE @DATE DATETIME
SET @DATE = '{{ Workflow | Attribute:'NextSundayDate' }}'

SELECT DATEPART(WEEK, @DATE)  -
    DATEPART(WEEK, DATEADD(MM, DATEDIFF(MM,0,@DATE), 0)) AS WEEK_OF_MONTH
